{"id": 2399, "genre": 1001, "title": "在生活中，你都听过哪些让人不太舒服的“丛林社会”式言论？", "description": "遵循丛林法则的社会是“本该如此”的吗？（图片来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 5294, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180606195417uYq9ZDMJXUQTAo5m.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-22T00:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 299776, "content": "没人没路子不行啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266931}, {"id": 299777, "content": "人要适应这个社会 变得圆滑 多交朋友 和领导打好关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374647}, {"id": 299778, "content": "落后就要挨打", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393374}, {"id": 299779, "content": "你现在得学会接触社会了 不然以后适应不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448808}, {"id": 304899, "content": "要大方一点多大点事儿嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474381}, {"id": 299780, "content": "学打麻将！迟早要学会的，不然不合群", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301880}, {"id": 300036, "content": "女人不生孩子是不完整得……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380411}, {"id": 302596, "content": "人家能做的你为什么不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098969}, {"id": 299781, "content": "事故一点，圆滑一点，你才能在职场生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564779}, {"id": 299782, "content": "你一女的 学这有嘛用？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 298, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390489}, {"id": 299783, "content": "女孩子要学会撒娇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294544}, {"id": 299784, "content": "爱情就要考虑经济", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405663}, {"id": 299785, "content": "女孩子要学会撒娇", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294544}, {"id": 300041